title: Show HN: Layoffbase – the place where you can get a new tech job after layoff
text:
I knew that layoffs in tech were coming. When it started, I've created Layoffbase to collect people without a job and help them get a new one. Now, I try to manually connect them with companies.

What do you think about it? How can I improve this?
